# {{name}}

A [Twill DB](https://github.com/bihaviour/twill-db) starter for **Bun** — a
serverless OLTP database embedded in-process via `bun:ffi`. No server to run, no
infrastructure to provision.

## Run it

```bash
bun install
bun run start
```

The native engine ships with `@twilldb/bun` as a per-platform optional
dependency, so there is no `cargo build` step. To point at a libengine you built
yourself, set `TWILLDB_ENGINE_PATH=/abs/path/libengine.{so,dylib,dll}`.

## Storage backend

The backend is chosen entirely by the connection string in `app.ts`:

| Scheme | Backend |
| --- | --- |
| `file://…` | embedded, persists to a local file (this starter's default) |
| `s3://` · `r2://` · `gs://` | storage-disaggregated; credentials come from the environment |

This project is configured for `{{db_url}}`.
